'''豐田Mirai'''（取自原日文「{{jp|j=未来|hg=ミライ|rm=Mirai}}」），是一款[[氫氣車|氫氣]][[燃料電池車|燃料電池汽車]]，也是全球首部商業販售的氫氣燃料電池汽車<ref name=transportevolved>{{cite web|url=http://transportevolved.com/2014/06/25/toyota-unveils-2015-fuel-cell-sedan-will-retail-japan-around-%C2%A57-million/|title=Toyota Unveils 2015 Fuel Cell Sedan, Will Retail in Japan For Around ¥7 Million|publisher=transportevolved.com|date=2014-06-25|accessdate=2014-06-26|archive-date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529150740/https://transportevolved.com/2014/06/25/toyota-unveils-2015-fuel-cell-sedan-will-retail-japan-around-%c2%a57-million/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name=ToyotaTech>{{cite web|url=http://www.toyota-global.com/innovation/environmental_technology/fuelcell_vehicle/|title=What is a Fuel Cell Vehicle?|accessdate=2014-08-06|archive-date=2015-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151231184855/http://www.toyota-global.com/innovation/environmental_technology/fuelcell_vehicle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Mirai車款在2014年11月[[洛杉磯國際車展|洛杉磯國際車展]]中亮相<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2014/11/20141117-mirai.html|title=Akio Toyoda announces name of Toyota’s new fuel cell sedan in web video: Mirai|first=Mike|last=Millikin|publisher=[[Green_Car_Congress|Green Car Congress]]|date=2014-11-17|accessdate=2014-11-17|archive-date=2016-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416022124/http://www.greencarcongress.com/2014/11/20141117-mirai.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，豐田汽車預計在2015年生產700輛以供應全球銷售<ref name=GCR112014>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarreports.com/news/1095511_2016-toyota-mirai-priced-at-57500-with-499-monthly-lease|title=2016 Toyota Mirai Priced At $57,500, With $499 Monthly Lease|author=John Voelcker|publisher=Green Car Reports|date=2014-11-18|accessdate=2014-11-19|archive-date=2014-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141118233932/http://www.greencarreports.com/news/1095511_2016-toyota-mirai-priced-at-57500-with-499-monthly-lease|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在美國環境保護政策下，這輛2016[[年度車款|年度車款]]Mirai在燃料全滿的情況下可以跑502公里（312英哩），城市/高速公路綜合燃料經濟評價獲得67mpg<sub>-US</sub>（3.5L/100km; 80mpg<sub>-imp</sub>），讓Mirai被EPA評為最具燃料效率的氫氣燃料電池車<ref name=FCVs>{{cite web|url=http://www.fueleconomy.gov/feg/fcv_sbs.shtml|title=Compare Fuel Cell Vehicles|website=fueleconomy.gov|author=[[United_States_Environmental_Protection_Agency|United States Environmental Protection Agency]] and [[U.S._Department_of_Energy|U.S. Department of Energy]]|date=2015-08-14|accessdate=2015-08-17|archive-date=2015-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150814215652/http://www.fueleconomy.gov/feg/fcv_sbs.shtml|dead-url=no}} ''One kg of hydrogen is roughly equivalent to one U.S. gallon of gasoline.''</ref>。

該車款於2014年12月15日開始在日本銷售，售價670万日元（約合57,400美元）。日本政府計劃以每台輔貼200万日元（约合19,600美元）的方式支持量產的燃料電池車<ref name=JapPrice>{{cite news|url=http://www.myfoxchicago.com/story/27410215/toyota-to-launch-fuel-cell-car-next-month|title=oyota to start sales of fuel cell car next month|author=Ken Moritsugu|work=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|publisher=Fox News Chicago|date=2014-11-18|accessdate=2014-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129040514/http://www.myfoxchicago.com/story/27410215/toyota-to-launch-fuel-cell-car-next-month|archivedate=2014-11-29}}</ref>。[[美國|美國]]上市時間預計為2015年8月，尚未扣除政府獎勵下每台售價57,500美元。一開始只打算在[[加州|加州]]販賣<ref name=GCR112014/><ref name=HC112014>{{cite web|url=http://www.hybridcars.com/toyota-mirai-to-be-priced-from-57500/|title=Toyota Mirai To Be Priced From $57,500|author=Jeff Cobb|publisher=HybridCars.com|date=2014-11-17|accessdate=2014-11-19|archive-date=2014-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141120231445/http://www.hybridcars.com/toyota-mirai-to-be-priced-from-57500/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歐洲市場預計2015年9月上市，一開始只在[[英國|英國]]、[[德國|德國]]、[[丹麥|丹麥]]等地销售，其他國家要等到2017年<ref name=ToyotaEU>{{cite press release|url=http://newsroom.toyota.eu/pressrelease/4124//toyota-ushers-future-launch-mirai-fuel-cell-sedan|title=Toyota Ushers In The Future With Launch Of ‘Mirai’ Fuel Cell Sedan|publisher=Toyota Europe|location=Toyota City, Japan|date=2014-11-01|accessdate=2014-11-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20141205173620/http://newsroom.toyota.eu/pressrelease/4124//toyota-ushers-future-launch-mirai-fuel-cell-sedan|archivedate=2014-12-05}}</ref>。德國定價為未稅6万欧元，含稅則為78,540欧元<ref name=ToyotaEU/>。

==歷史==

{{anchor|FCV}}
===FCV概念車===
Mirai源於豐田FCV（取自Fuel Cell Vehicle英文縮寫，譯為「燃料電池車」）[[概念車|概念車]]，FCV於2013年[[東京車展|東京車展]]中首度亮相<ref name=Tokyo2013>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/21/business/international/toyota-unveils-fuel-cell-concept-automobile.html?_r=0 |title=Toyota Shows Off Fuel-Cell Automobile |date=2013-11-20 |accessdate=2014-06-27 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104175703/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/21/business/international/toyota-unveils-fuel-cell-concept-automobile.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其水滴狀外型亮藍色房車概念，藉以彰顯「水是從氫氣動力汽車排氣管所排放的唯一物質」。FCV的大型進氣格柵和其他開口，有利於導入冷空氣和氧氣，供[[燃料電池|燃料電池]]使用。豐田汽車表示這款FCV概念車外觀很接近市場預期的量產化版本<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/21/business/international/toyota-unveils-fuel-cell-concept-automobile.html?|title=Toyota Shows Off Fuel-Cell Automobile|author=Eric Pfanner|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2013-11-20|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2014-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202081443/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/21/business/international/toyota-unveils-fuel-cell-concept-automobile.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，FCV車體尺寸和[[豐田Camry|豐田Camry]]車款相似<ref name=Bloomberg1>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-25/toyota-to-offer-69-000-car-as-musk-pans-fool-cells-.html/|title=Toyota to Offer $69,000 Car After Musk Pans ‘Fool Cells’|date=2014-06-25|accessdate=2014-06-27|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627055520/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-25/toyota-to-offer-69-000-car-as-musk-pans-fool-cells-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。參照日本{{link-ja|JC08模式|JC08モード}}測試，FCV的[[汽車燃油經濟性|汽車燃油經濟性]]總里程可達約700公里（430英里）<ref name=Toyotapresentation>{{cite web|url=http://newsroom.toyota.co.jp/en/download/3332962|title=Toyota's Approach to Fuel Cell Vehicles|date=2014-06-25|accessdate=2014-06-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629151703/http://newsroom.toyota.co.jp/en/download/3332962|archivedate=2014-06-29}}</ref>。
[[File:2013_Toyota_FCV_CONCEPT_01.jpg|thumb]]
豐田汽車表示FCV另一特點為擁有 3.0 kW/L 輸出動力密度的燃料電池系統，比前一代燃料電池概念車FCHV-adv可輸出100 kW動力，提升了二倍之多，儘管FCV已將各部品單元明顯小型化。FCV採用豐田汽車專利的小型輕量化燃料電池堆疊技術以及配置於設計車體下方的70[[帕斯卡|MPa]]高壓[[氫氣箱|氫氣箱]]。豐田FCV概念車可容納四名乘員，2015年全面量產上市時，預期其燃料電池系統成本將比2008年豐田FCHV-adv概念車低達95%<ref name=GCC032014>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2014/03/20140311-fcv.html|title=Toyota continues to prepare the market for fuel cell vehicle in 2015|author=Mike Millikin|publisher=[[Green_Car_Congress|Green Car Congress]]|date=2014-03-11|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129023141/http://www.greencarcongress.com/2014/03/20140311-fcv.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

FCV概念車也採用豐田汽車的[[油電複合動力系統|油電複合動力]]技術，包括：[[馬達|電動馬達]]、動力控制單元、和其他來自複合動力汽車的零組件，以改善可靠度，以及成本最小化<ref name=GCC032014/>。複合動力技術亦被採用於燃料電池協同運作。低速時(例如駕駛於市區內)，FCV如同[[電動汽車|電動汽車]]以儲存於車身電池之電能運轉，該電池利用[[再生軔機|煞車制動再生]]充電；高速時氫氣燃料電池則獨自驅動電動馬達。當需求更多動力時(例如：突然加速期間)，電池支援燃料電池系統協同運作，以供應充足動力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.toyota-europe.com/world-of-toyota/environmental-technology/fuel-cell-technology.json|title=Fuel Cell Technology - Another step towards sustainable mobility|author=Toyota Europe|publisher=Toyota Europe|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129053546/http://www.toyota-europe.com/world-of-toyota/environmental-technology/fuel-cell-technology.json|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年6月豐田汽車展示一輛外觀設計接近量產車的FCV車款，並宣布日本定價細目，訂於2015年4月於日本國內發表上市，僅限於氫氣加氣基礎設施已開發完成區域<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2014/06/20140625-fcv.html|title=Toyota to launch its fuel cell vehicle in Japan before April 2015, priced around $68,700; reveals exterior|author=Mike Millikin|publisher=[[Green_Car_Congress|Green Car Congress]]|date=2014-06-25|accessdate=2014-11-17|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129022339/http://www.greencarcongress.com/2014/06/20140625-fcv.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

