{{As of|2013|01}}，日本已擁有10座示範的[[氫氣加氣站|氫氣加氣站]]<ref>[http://www.fuelcelltoday.com/news-archive/2013/january/jx-energy-planning-40-hydrogen-refuelling-stations-in-japan-by-2015 "JX Energy Planning 40 Hydrogen Refuelling Stations in Japan by 2015"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fuelcelltoday.com/news-archive/2013/january/jx-energy-planning-40-hydrogen-refuelling-stations-in-japan-by-2015 |date=20151210235725 }}, FuelCellToday.com, January 14, 2013, accessed June 27, 2014</ref>，豐田汽車經營其中的3個加氣站<ref name=Toyotcorp>{{cite web|url=http://www.toyota-global.com/innovation/environmental_technology/fuelcell_vehicle//|title=A vehicle running on hydrogen|date=|accessdate=2014-06-27|archive-date=2014-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626122832/http://www.toyota-global.com/innovation/environmental_technology/fuelcell_vehicle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，支援豐田汽車和其他製造商的氫氣燃料電池車的商業化用途。日本政府也宣布2016年3月在日本首批氫氣燃料電池車規劃上市的地點，將建造大約100座氫氣加氣站的目標<ref>[http://profit.ndtv.com/news/corporates/article-japan-bets-big-on-making-fuel-cell-cars-a-near-future-reality-571779 "Japan Bets Big on Making Fuel-Cell Cars a Near-Future Reality"] {{Wayback|url=http://profit.ndtv.com/news/corporates/article-japan-bets-big-on-making-fuel-cell-cars-a-near-future-reality-571779 |date=20151211042239 }}, Reuters, NDTV.com, June 25, 2014</ref>。美國加州也有10座氫氣加氣站，州政府將提供4700萬美元資金建造另28座氫氣加氣站<ref name=Bloomberg1/>。

==生產製造==

2014年11月在[[豐田紡織株式會社|豐田紡織株式會社]]的工廠開始製造燃料電池組件<ref name="#1">{{cite press release|url=http://www.automotiveworld.com/news-releases/toyota-boshoku-starts-production-fuel-cell-parts-applying-proprietary-technologies/|title=Toyota Boshoku starts production of Fuel Cell parts by applying its proprietary technologies|author=Toyota|publisher=Automotive World|location=Tokyo|date=2014-11-21|accessdate=2014-11-22|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923180606/http://www.automotiveworld.com/news-releases/toyota-boshoku-starts-production-fuel-cell-parts-applying-proprietary-technologies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，車輛組裝工序則於豐田市元町工場進行。

